00:01:31,100 --> 00:01:35,260
 but we are in response, in obedience

42
00:01:35,260 --> 00:01:37,200
 to what God has called us to do.

43
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:39,100
 Even if it's not comfortable,

44
00:01:39,100 --> 00:01:41,840
 we were challenged to go and to obey.

45
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:45,600
 And then we talked about shifting our perspective

