00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:11,340
 in different places of the world are facing today.

58
00:02:11,340 --> 00:02:12,420
 And the challenge there was,

59
00:02:12,420 --> 00:02:14,100
 when we do face persecution,

60
00:02:14,100 --> 00:02:16,520
 not to shrink back, not to shy away,

