00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:15,340
 to testify near and far about who Jesus is.

108
00:04:15,340 --> 00:04:17,700
 This is our mission.

109
00:04:17,700 --> 00:04:20,840
 This has always been the mission of the church,

110
00:04:20,840 --> 00:04:23,000
 of the people of God.

